INSERT INTO techtrek_db.job_listings (id, apply_url, description, is_archived, is_remote, listing_date, location, title, company_id) VALUES (30, 'http://techtrek.dev', '<span style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline: 0px;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline: 0px;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit;">Job Description</span><br style="box-sizing: inherit;"><br style="box-sizing: inherit;"></span>This position provides support to the 47th Cyberspace Test Squadron (CTS) – Located at Joint Base San Antonio, TX. This support includes the following:<br style="box-sizing: inherit;"><ul style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 16px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 18px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.42857;"><li style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.42857;">Provide test automation research, development, test, and evaluation support for all phases of test automation as the recognized technical experts on Network Warfare test capabilities</li><li style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.42857;">Software Engineering support will cover entire test automation conception, emerging research and test to fielding decisions.</li><li style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.42857;">Research, design, develop, and/or modify test automation using various industry tools for systems and/or applications software</li><li style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.42857;">Planning of system automation deployment as well as responsible for meeting software compliance standards</li><li style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.42857;">Evaluates interface between hardware and software, operational requirements, and characteristics of overall system</li><li style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.42857;">Documents testing and maintenance of system corrections</li><li style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.42857;">Test automation (Jenkins, Robot Framework, Selenium, etc…)</li><li style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.42857;">Operating systems (Linux, Windows, etc…)</li><li style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.42857;">Software Development methodologies (agile, waterfall, etc…)</li><li style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.42857;">Scripting and other languages (Shell, Python, JavaScript, UML, AJAX, JSON, BASH, PowerShell, Power CLI)</li><li style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.42857;">Development tools and services, any current IDE, notepad++, VS Code, GIT</li><li style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.42857;">Basic understanding of Software Security</li><li style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.42857;">Op Open Source, cloud and virtualization software and services</li><br style="box-sizing: inherit;"><br style="box-sizing: inherit;"></ul><font face="-apple-system, system-ui, system-ui, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica Neue, Fira Sans, Ubuntu, Oxygen, Oxygen Sans, Cantarell, Droid Sans, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji, Segoe UI Symbol, Lucida Grande, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-color: initial; outline-style: initial;">At COLSA, people are our most valuable resource and centered at our core value. We invite you to unite your talents with opportunity and be a part of our “Family of Professionals!” Learn about our employee-centric culture and benefits</span></font><br style="box-sizing: inherit;"><br style="box-sizing: inherit;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline: 0px;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit;">Required Experience</span><br style="box-sizing: inherit;"><br style="box-sizing: inherit;"></span><span style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline: 0px;">One of the following combinations is required:&nbsp;</span>Master’s Degree and a minimum of 10 years of applicable experience -OR- Bachelor’s degree and 18 years of applicable experience –OR- HS Diploma or Equivalent and 22 years of applicable experience.<br style="box-sizing: inherit;"><ul style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 16px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 18px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.42857;"><li style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.42857;">Minimum of 5 years of software engineering/related experience--to include software development</li><li style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.42857;">Knowledge of Waterfall &amp; Agile software development methodologies</li><li style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.42857;">US Citizenship required. Must be able to obtain/maintain DoD clearance. Current Active DOD Clearance preferred.</li><li style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.42857;">Obtain DOD 8570 IAT Level 2 certification or higher within 6 months of hire, and maintain certification throughout employment</li><li style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.42857;">Analytical skills and problem solving skills in the area of software engineering</li><li style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.42857;">Good organization, decision making, and verbal and written communication skills.</li><li style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.42857;">Excellent self-initiative and self-motivation with the ability to work under minimal supervision</li><br style="box-sizing: inherit;"><br style="box-sizing: inherit;"></ul><font face="-apple-system, system-ui, system-ui, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica Neue, Fira Sans, Ubuntu, Oxygen, Oxygen Sans, Cantarell, Droid Sans, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji, Segoe UI Symbol, Lucida Grande, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline-color: initial; outline-style: initial;">Applicant selected will be subject to a government security investigation and must meet eligibility requirements for access to classified information. COLSA Corporation is an Equal Opportunity Employer, Minorities/Females/Veterans/Disabled. All qualified applicants will receive consideration for employment without regard to race, color, religion, sex, sexual orientation, gender identity, or national origin.</span></font></span><div id="ember1300" class="jobs-description-details pt4 pt4 ember-view" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; columns: auto 2; padding-top: 16px !important;"><div class="jobs-box__group" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; break-inside: avoid;"><h3 class="jobs-box__sub-title js-formatted-industries-title" style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline: 0px; line-height: 1.42857;"><br></h3></div></div>', false, 0, '2020-06-08 06:03:44.237000', 'San Antonio, Texas', 'Staff Software Engineer', 1);
INSERT INTO techtrek_db.job_listings (id, apply_url, description, is_archived, is_remote, listing_date, location, title, company_id) VALUES (31, 'http://google.com', '<p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 1.4rem; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; line-height: 1.42857; font-weight: 400; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);"><strong style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; outline: 0px; font-weight: 600;">About&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 22.4px; font-weight: 400;">Aviato</span>&nbsp;Systems, Inc</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 1.4rem; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; line-height: 1.42857; font-weight: 400; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);">At Aviato we are committed to delivering trusted expertise to our government clients.&nbsp;As we grow, our focus is on increasing opportunities for you to grow with us while still delivering the same excellence customers have grown to expect from us.&nbsp;We continually evaluate our environment to provide a place where your career is packed with opportunities to grow and you have the ability to demonstrate your passion to our customers.&nbsp;We focus on building a Team where each employee is a valued member.&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 22.4px;">Aviato</span>&nbsp;provides support to multiple agencies across the United States Government in many locations. That means many different opportunities to follow your career path without changing companies every few years.</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 1.4rem; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; line-height: 1.42857; font-weight: 400; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);"><br style="box-sizing: inherit;"></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 1.4rem; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; line-height: 1.42857; font-weight: 400; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);"><strong style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; outline: 0px; font-weight: 600;">"Employee driven...mission focused."&nbsp;We build, operate and secure networks and infrastructure</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 1.4rem; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; line-height: 1.42857; font-weight: 400; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);"><br style="box-sizing: inherit;"></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 1.4rem; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; line-height: 1.42857; font-weight: 400; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);"><strong style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; outline: 0px; font-weight: 600;">What you will do</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 1.4rem; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; line-height: 1.42857; font-weight: 400; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);">Respond to internal and external IT Service Requests for IT service on both Unix and NT servers. Provide user notification of receipt of Web- or email-submitted requests. Logs and tracks inquiries using service request management database, and maintains history records and related documentation.&nbsp;Promptly categorizes, generates, routes and escalates, when necessary, customer requests that are escalated beyond the ITSC area of responsibility.&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 1.4rem; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; line-height: 1.42857; font-weight: 400; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;